{"id":1546,"category_slug":"toeic","category_name":"TOEIC Listening","position":324,"title":"Conversation 164","subtitle":"Lost Luggage Inquiry","level":"B1","parts":16,"url":"https://dailydictation.com/exercises/toeic/conversation-164.1546/listen-and-type","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/0-conversation-164.mp3","transcript":"Excuse me,\nI was on flight TR6 from Tokyo,\nbut none of my checked bags have shown up yet.\nMay I see your tags, please?\nHuh?\nWhat tags?\nThey should be stuck to the back of your ticket.\nThey're little stickers with a barcodes on them.\nOh, yeah.\nHere you go.\nHmm... It looks like your bags were sent to Chicago somehow!\nI'm sorry about the mix-up.\nThey won't make it here today, but we can ship them to you by tomorrow.\nAre you sure they'll arrive by tomorrow?\nYes.\nJust give me your address, and we will deliver your bags to your house by noon.","youtube_video_id":"","details_cached_at":"2026-06-15T21:02:34","challenges":[{"position":1,"content":"Excuse me,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/1.mp3","time_start":0.31,"time_end":1.76},{"position":2,"content":"I was on flight TR6 from Tokyo,","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/2.mp3","time_start":1.89,"time_end":5.15},{"position":3,"content":"but none of my checked bags have shown up yet.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/3.mp3","time_start":5.15,"time_end":8.41},{"position":4,"content":"May I see your tags, please?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/4.mp3","time_start":8.41,"time_end":10.34},{"position":5,"content":"Huh?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/5.mp3","time_start":10.34,"time_end":11.12},{"position":6,"content":"What tags?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/6.mp3","time_start":11.63,"time_end":12.6},{"position":7,"content":"They should be stuck to the back of your ticket.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/7.mp3","time_start":12.6,"time_end":15.14},{"position":8,"content":"They're little stickers with a barcodes on them.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/8.mp3","time_start":15.37,"time_end":17.89},{"position":9,"content":"Oh, yeah.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/9.mp3","time_start":17.89,"time_end":19.05},{"position":10,"content":"Here you go.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/10.mp3","time_start":19.47,"time_end":20.56},{"position":11,"content":"Hmm... It looks like your bags were sent to Chicago somehow!","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/11.mp3","time_start":20.83,"time_end":25.56},{"position":12,"content":"I'm sorry about the mix-up.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/12.mp3","time_start":25.56,"time_end":27.8},{"position":13,"content":"They won't make it here today, but we can ship them to you by tomorrow.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/13.mp3","time_start":27.99,"time_end":32.01},{"position":14,"content":"Are you sure they'll arrive by tomorrow?","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/14.mp3","time_start":32.01,"time_end":34.2},{"position":15,"content":"Yes.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/15.mp3","time_start":34.2,"time_end":34.95},{"position":16,"content":"Just give me your address, and we will deliver your bags to your house by noon.","audio_url":"https://dailydictation.com/upload/toeic/conversation-164-2024-09-14-18-31-23/16.mp3","time_start":34.95,"time_end":39.24}]}